packets.name: PIXLwear P1 Sneaker “Deep Ocean”, right
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description: The PIXLwear P1 sneaker is a Cryptovoxels shoe for every situation. Comfortable, yet stylish. High-quality, yet affordable. The P1 model rocks the iconic PIXLwear colours for the tie-free laces and the PIXL P1 stamp on the sole. The insoles are also stamped with “P” and “1” on the left and right shoe, respectively. This is the right shoe from the “Deep Ocean” edition. Designer: Pixls.eth. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear: a PIXL brand - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
